1. Ona *ostavlja* svoju jaknu u garderobi. (She leaves her jacket in the cloakroom.)
2. Nikada ne *ostavljam* važne stvari za poslednji trenutak. (I never leave important things for the last minute.)
3. Ova knjiga *ostavlja* dubok utisak na čitaoca. (This book leaves a deep impression on the reader.)
4. Da li ste *ostavili* ključeve u bravi? (Did you leave the keys in the lock?)
5. On *ostavlja* dobar utisak na svoje kolege. (He leaves a good impression on his colleagues.)
6. Nisam siguran da li sam *ostavio* novac na stolu. (I'm not sure if I left the money on the table.)
7. Ta odluka *ostavlja* ozbiljne posledice po našu budućnost. (That decision has serious consequences for our future.)
8. Kako *ostaviti* loš dojam na prvom sastanku. (How to make a bad impression on the first date.)
9. Moramo *ostaviti* prošlost iza sebe i krenuti dalje. (We have to leave the past behind and move on.)
10. Oni *ostavljaju* sve svoje brige na teret drugih ljudi. (They leave all their worries on the shoulders of other people.)